  body
    .fh5co-loader
    #page
      nav.fh5co-nav(role='navigation')
        .container
          .row
            .col-xs-2
              #fh5co-logo
                a(href='index.html')
                  | Wedding
                  strong .
            .col-xs-10.text-right.menu-1
              ul
                li.active
                  a(href='index') Home
                li
                  a(href='/users/rsvp') RSVP
                
      header#fh5co-header.fh5co-cover(role='banner', style='background-image:url(images/img_bg_2.jpg);', data-stellar-background-ratio='0.5')
        .overlay
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center
              .display-t
                .display-tc.animate-box(data-animate-effect='fadeIn')
                  h1 Kartikay & Aarushi
                  h2 We Are Getting Married
                  .simply-countdown.simply-countdown-one
                  p
                    a.btn.btn-default.btn-sm(href='/users/rsvp') RSVP
      #fh5co-couple
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center.fh5co-heading.animate-box
              h2 Hello!
              h3 February 28th, 2017 New Delhi
              p We invited you to celebrate our wedding
          .couple-wrap.animate-box
            .couple-half
              .groom
                img.img-responsive(src='images/Lucu.jpg', alt='groom')
              .desc-groom
                h3 Kartikay Sharma
                p
                  | Flamboyant kind. Living life large and having fun is what its all about. Love working hard and partying harder
                  My better half info is on the right
            .couple-half
              .bride
                img.img-responsive(src='images/Aarushi.jpg', alt='groom')
              .desc-bride
                h3 Aarushi Sharma
                p
                  | Fun loving kind. When I'm not working hard or watching TV shows, I'm blaming my better half for whatever goes
                  goes wrong in my life 
      #fh5co-event.fh5co-bg(style='background-image:url(images/weddingEvents.jpg);')
        .overlay
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center.fh5co-heading.animate-box
              span Our Special Events
              h2 Wedding Events
          .row
            .display-t
              .display-tc
                .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
                  .col-md-6.col-sm-6.text-center
                    .event-wrap.animate-box
                      h3 Cocktails Event
                      .event-col
                        i.icon-clock
                        span 4:00 PM
                        span 6:00 PM
                      .event-col
                        i.icon-calendar
                        span Monday 28
                        span November, 2016
                      p
                        | Ernest Hemingay quoted "An intelligent man is sometimes forced to be drunk to spend time with his fools"
                        So if you think you're intelligent, gear up for some liquid courage
                      p
                        | Join us at Club Patio, Block E, South City 1, Heritage City
                        Gurgaon

                  .col-md-6.col-sm-6.text-center
                    .event-wrap.animate-box
                      h3 Wedding Party
                      .event-col
                        i.icon-clock
                        span 8:00 PM
                        span 2:00 AM  
                      .event-col
                        i.icon-calendar
                        span Monday 28
                        span November, 2016
                      p
                        | I now pronounce you husband and wife. You may now update your Facebook status.
                        Drinks and Dinner are on the house btw so do not miss this once in a lifetime opportunity
                      p
                        | Join us at The Open Terrace, Pllazio Hotel, City Center, Sector 29
                        Gurgaon
                  
      #fh5co-couple-story
        .container
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.text-center.fh5co-heading.animate-box
              span We Love Each Other
              h2 Our Story
              p
                | Far far away, behind the word mountains, far from the countries Vokalia and Consonantia, there live the blind texts.
          .row
            .col-md-12.col-md-offset-0
              ul.timeline.animate-box
                li.animate-box
                  .timeline-badge(style='background-image:url(images/FirstMet.jpg);')
                  .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                      h3.timeline-title First We Met
                      span.date December 31, 2011
                    .timeline-body
                      p
                        | Who knew that a simple new year's eve house party could prove to be one of the most decisive
                        moments in our lives
                li.timeline-inverted.animate-box
                  .timeline-badge(style='background-image:url(images/relationship.jpg);')
                  .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                      h3.timeline-title First Date
                      span.date January 15, 2012
                    .timeline-body
                      p
                        | Didn't take long for our new year's eve wishes to be with each other come in effect even though he ended 
                        up taking her to McDonalds 
                li.animate-box
                  .timeline-badge(style='background-image:url(images/proposal.jpg);')
                  .timeline-panel
                    .timeline-heading
                      h3.timeline-title Engagement
                      span.date January 1, 2016
                    .timeline-body
                      p
                        | The year could not have started in a better way than this than him embarrasing himself by falling on his face. 
                        So beautiful yet hilarious
     
        
